Exxaro's executive head of projects and technology Johan Meyer spoke to Mining Review Editor Africa Laura Cornish at this year's Investing in African Mining Indaba and shared with her some of the exciting initiatives the company is currently working on. These include the development of South Africa's first truly digital mine and a R20 billion investment in new projects in the country. "We are truly committed to empowering better lives and promoting a better future for the country," Meyer higlights.